gmd:CI_DateTypeCode/revision/description: 자원이 검토, 재검토, 개선 또는 개정 되었을때 날짜 확인
gmd:CI_OnLineFunctionCode/download/descr: 다른 저장장치 또는 다른 시스템으로 데이타를 전송하기위한 온라인 지침
gmd:CI_OnLineFunctionCode/offlineAccess/: 공급자로부터 자원을 요청하기 위한 온라인 지침
gmd:CI_OnLineFunctionCode/order/descript: 자원을 획득하기 위한 온라인 주문 절차
gmd:CI_OnLineFunctionCode/search/descrip: 자원에 대한 정보를 찾기위한 온라인 검색 인터페이스
gmd:CI_PresentationFormCode/documentDigi: 주요 텍스트 항목의 디지털 표현(이미지가 포함될 수 있음)
gmd:CI_PresentationFormCode/imageDigital: 디지털 형식의 시각적 감지 또는 열 적외선 및 고해상도 레이더 등의 센서에 의한 전자기 스펙트럼의 다른 부분을 통해 획득되고 저장 천연 또는 인공의 특징, 목적 및 활동의 모습
gmd:CI_PresentationFormCode/documentHard: 종이문서, 사진 메체, 또는 다른 미디어에 대한 주요 텍스트 항목의 표현(이미지가 포함 될 수 있음)
gmd:CI_PresentationFormCode/imageHardcop: 자연적인 관계 또는 인간이 만든 형상, 객체, 그리고 시각적 감각을 통해서 얻어지는 활동 또는 센서에 의한 전자기적 스펙트럼의 다름 부분, 열적외선 과 같은, 그리고 고해상도 레이다 그리고 종이문서, 사진 미디어, 인간에 의해 직접적으로 사용되는 다른 미디어에 대해 재현되는 것
gmd:CI_PresentationFormCode/mapHardcopy/: 인간에 의해 직접적으로 사용 된 종이, 사진 재료, 또는 다른 매체에 인쇄 된 맵
gmd:CI_PresentationFormCode/modelDigital: 형상, 절차, 기타 등의 다차원 디지털 표현
gmd:CI_PresentationFormCode/tableDigital: 체계적으로 표시된 형체 또는 사실의 디지털 표현, 특히 컬럼으로
gmd:CI_PresentationFormCode/tableHardcop: 사실 또는 형체의 체계적 표현, 특히 컬럼, 종이에 인쇄, 사진 매체, 또는 다른 매체
gmd:CI_RoleCode/custodian/description: 데이터에 대한 책임과 의무를 수락하고 자원의 적절한 관리 및 유지 보수를 보장 하는 단체
gmd:CI_RoleCode/pointOfContact/descripti: 자원의 인수 또는 지식의 취득을 위해 연락 할 수 있는 단체
gmd:CI_RoleCode/principalInvestigator/de: 정보를 수집하고 연구를 수행 할 책임이 있는 주요 단체
gmd:CI_RoleCode/processor/description: 수정된 자원과 같은 방법으로 데이터를 처리하는 단체

			evaluated
gmd:DQ_EvaluationMethodTypeCode/directEx:
Method of evaluating the quality of a dataset based on inspection of items
				within the dataset, where reference data external to the dataset being evaluated is
				required
gmd:DQ_EvaluationMethodTypeCode/indirect: 외부 지식에 기반 하는 데이터 집합의 품질 평가 방법

Mapping and charting information from which the dataset content

gmd:DS_AssociationTypeCode/stereoMate/de:
Part of a set of imagery that when used together, provides three-dimensional
				images

gmd:DS_InitiativeTypeCode/exercise/descr: Specific performance of a function or group of functions

gmd:DS_InitiativeTypeCode/operation/desc: Action that is part of a series of actions
gmd:DS_InitiativeTypeCode/platform/descr: Vehicle or other support base that holds a sensor
gmd:DS_InitiativeTypeCode/process/descri: Method of doing something involving a number of steps
gmd:DS_InitiativeTypeCode/trial/descript: Process of testing to discover or demonstrate something

ISO/IEC 8859-7, Information technology - 8-bit single byte coded graphic

gmd:MD_CharacterSetCode/8859part8/descri:
ISO/IEC 8859-8, Information technology - 8-bit single byte coded graphic

gmd:MD_CharacterSetCode/8859part9/descri: ISO/IEC 8859-9, Information technology - 8-bit 1바이트 코드 그래픽 문자 셋 - Part 9 : 라틴 알파벳 No.5

gmd:MD_CharacterSetCode/8859part16/descr: ISO/IEC 8859-16, Information technology - 8-bit 1바이트 코드 그래픽 문자 셋 - Part 16 : 라틴 알파벳 No.10

gmd:MD_CharacterSetCode/eucJP/descriptio: UNIX기반 머신에서 사용되는 일본 코드 셋
gmd:MD_CharacterSetCode/usAscii/descript: United States ASCII code set (ISO 646 US)
gmd:MD_CharacterSetCode/big5/description:
Traditional Chinese code set used in Taiwan, Hong Kong of China and other
				areas
gmd:MD_ClassificationCode/secret/descrip: 선택된 사람들의 그룹을 제외하고 모든 것으로 부터 보호되거나 개인적으로 보호, 알려지지 않은, 숨겨진
gmd:MD_CoverageContentTypeCode/image/des:
Meaningful numerical representation of a physical parameter that is not the
				actual value of the physical parameter
gmd:MD_CoverageContentTypeCode/thematicC:
Code value with no quantitative meaning, used to represent a physical
			quantity
gmd:MD_CoverageContentTypeCode/physicalM: Value in physical units of the quantity being measured
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/class/description:
Descriptor of a set of objects that share the same attributes, operations,
				methods, relationships, and behavior
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/codelist/description:
Descriptor of a set of objects that share the same attributes, operations,
				methods, relationships, and behavior
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/enumeration/descript:
Data type whose instances form a list of named literal values, not
			extendable
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/codelistElement/desc: Permissible value for a codelist or enumeration
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/abstractClass/descri: Class that cannot be directly instantiated
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/aggregateClass/descr:
Class that is composed of classes it is connected to by an aggregate
				relationship
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/specifiedClass/descr: Subclass that may be substituted for its superclass
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/datatypeClass/descri:
Class with few or no operations whose primary purpose is to hold the abstract
				state of another class for transmittal, storage, encoding or persistent
			storage
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/interfaceClass/descr:
Named set of operations that characterize the behavior of an
			element
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/unionClass/descripti: Class describing a selection of one of the specified types
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/typeClass/descriptio:
Class used for specification of a domain of instances (objects), together with
				the operations applicable to the objects. A type may have attributes and
			associations
gmd:MD_DatatypeCode/association/descript:
Semantic relationship between two classes that involves connections among
				their instances
gmd:MD_DimensionNameTypeCode/track/descr: Along the direction of motion of the scan point
gmd:MD_DimensionNameTypeCode/crossTrack/: Perpendicular to the direction of motion of the scan point
gmd:MD_GeometricObjectTypeCode/complex/d:
Set of geometric primitives such that their boundaries can be represented as a
				union of other primitives
gmd:MD_GeometricObjectTypeCode/composite: 커브 집합의 연결, 선 또는 면
gmd:MD_GeometricObjectTypeCode/curve/des:
Bounded, 1-dimensional geometric primitive, representing the continuous image
				of a line
gmd:MD_GeometricObjectTypeCode/point/des:
Zero-dimensional geometric primitive, representing a position but not having
				an extent
gmd:MD_GeometricObjectTypeCode/solid/des:
Bounded, connected 3-dimensional geometric primitive, representing the
				continuous image of a region of space
gmd:MD_GeometricObjectTypeCode/surface/d:
Bounded, connected 2-dimensional geometric primitive, representing the
				continuous image of a region of a plane
gmd:MD_ImagingConditionCode/cloud/descri: Portion of the image is partially obscured by cloud cover
gmd:MD_ImagingConditionCode/degradingObl:
Acute angle between the plane of the ecliptic (the plane of the Earth s orbit)
				and the plane of the celestial equator
gmd:MD_ImagingConditionCode/fog/descript: Portion of the image is partially obscured by fog
gmd:MD_ImagingConditionCode/heavySmokeOr:
Portion of the image is partially obscured by heavy smoke or
			dust
gmd:MD_ImagingConditionCode/semiDarkness: 중간정도 어둔움, 일몰 시에 촬영된 이미지
gmd:MD_ImagingConditionCode/terrainMaski:
The absence of collection data of a given point or area caused by the relative
				location of topographic features which obstruct the collection path between the
				collector(s) and the subject(s) of interest
gmd:MD_KeywordTypeCode/discipline/descri:
Keyword identifies a branch of instruction or specialized
			learning
gmd:MD_KeywordTypeCode/stratum/descripti: Keyword identifies the layer(s) of any deposited substance
gmd:MD_KeywordTypeCode/temporal/descript: Keyword identifies a time period related to the dataset
gmd:MD_KeywordTypeCode/theme/description: Keyword identifies a particular subject or topic
gmd:MD_MaintenanceFrequencyCode/continua: Data is repeatedly and frequently updated
gmd:MD_MaintenanceFrequencyCode/weekly/d: Data is updated on a weekly basis
gmd:MD_MaintenanceFrequencyCode/fortnigh: Data is updated every two weeks
gmd:MD_MaintenanceFrequencyCode/quarterl: Data is updated every three months
gmd:MD_MaintenanceFrequencyCode/biannual: Data is updated twice each year
gmd:MD_MaintenanceFrequencyCode/asNeeded: Data is updated as deemed necessary
gmd:MD_MaintenanceFrequencyCode/irregula: Data is updated in intervals that are uneven in duration
gmd:MD_MediumFormatCode/cpio/description: CoPy In / Out (UNIX 파일 포맷과 명령어)
gmd:MD_MediumFormatCode/iso9660/descript: CD-ROM의 정보 처리 볼륨 및 파일 구조
gmd:MD_PixelOrientationCode/center/descr:
Point halfway between the lower left and the upper right of the
			pixel
gmd:MD_PixelOrientationCode/lowerLeft/de:
The corner in the pixel closest to the origin of the SRS; if two are at the
				same distance from the origin, the one with the smallest x-value
gmd:MD_PixelOrientationCode/lowerRight/d: Next corner counterclockwise from the lower left
gmd:MD_PixelOrientationCode/upperRight/d: Next corner counterclockwise from the lower right
gmd:MD_PixelOrientationCode/upperLeft/de: Next corner counterclockwise from the upper right
gmd:MD_ProgressCode/completed/descriptio: Production of the data has been completed
gmd:MD_ProgressCode/historicalArchive/de: Data has been stored in an offline storage facility
gmd:MD_ProgressCode/planned/description:
Fixed date has been established upon or by which the data will be created or
				updated
gmd:MD_RestrictionCode/copyright/descrip:
Exclusive right to the publication, production, or sale of the rights to a
				literary, dramatic, musical, or artistic work, or to the use of a commercial print or
				label, granted by law for a specified period of time to an author, composer, artist,
				distributor
gmd:MD_RestrictionCode/patent/descriptio:
Government has granted exclusive right to make, sell, use or license an
				invention or discovery
gmd:MD_RestrictionCode/patentPending/des: Produced or sold information awaiting a patent
gmd:MD_RestrictionCode/trademark/descrip:
A name, symbol, or other device identifying a product, officially registered
				and legally restricted to the use of the owner or manufacturer
gmd:MD_RestrictionCode/intellectualPrope:
Rights to financial benefit from and control of distribution of non-tangible
				property that is a result of creativity
gmd:MD_RestrictionCode/restricted/descri: Withheld from general circulation or disclosure
gmd:MD_ScopeCode/software/description: 컴퓨터 프로그램 또는 루틴에 적용되는 정보
gmd:MD_ScopeCode/service/description: 정보는 서비스 공급자 엔티티는  유스 케이스와 같은 동작을 정의하는 인터페이스 세트를 통해 서비스 사용자 엔티티에 제공하는 기능에 적용됩니다
gmd:MD_ScopeCode/model/description: 정보는 기존 또는 가상 객체의 복사 또는 모방에 적용됩니다.
gmd:MD_ScopeCode/tile/description: 정보는 타일에 지리 데이터의 공간적인 부분 집합을 적용합니다
gmd:MD_SpatialRepresentationTypeCode/vec: 지리정보를 표현하기 위해 벡터 데이터가 사용됨
gmd:MD_SpatialRepresentationTypeCode/gri: 지리정보를 표현하기 위해 래스터 데이터가 사용됨
gmd:MD_SpatialRepresentationTypeCode/tex: 지리정보를 표현하기 위해 텍스트 또는 테이블 데이터가 사용됨
gmd:MD_SpatialRepresentationTypeCode/ste:
Three-dimensional view formed by the intersecting homologous rays of an
				overlapping pair of images
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/farming/descrip:
Rearing of animals and/or cultivation of plants. Examples: agriculture,
				irrigation, aquaculture, plantations, herding, pests and diseases affecting crops and
				livestock
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/biota/descripti:
Flora and/or fauna in natural environment. Examples: wildlife, vegetation,
				biological sciences, ecology, wilderness, sealife, wetlands, habitat
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/boundaries/desc:
Legal land descriptions. Examples: political and administrative
			boundaries
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/climatologyMete:
Processes and phenomena of the atmosphere. Examples: cloud cover, weather,
				climate, atmospheric conditions, climate change, precipitation
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/economy/descrip:
Economic activities, conditions and employment. Examples: production, labour,
				revenue, commerce, industry, tourism and ecotourism, forestry, fisheries, commercial or
				subsistence hunting, exploration and exploitation of resources such as minerals, oil and
				gas
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/elevation/descr:
Height above or below sea level. Examples: altitude, bathymetry, digital
				elevation models, slope, derived products
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/environment/des:
Environmental resources, protection and conservation. Examples: environmental
				pollution, waste storage and treatment, environmental impact assessment, monitoring
				environmental risk, nature reserves, landscape
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/geoscientificIn:
Information pertaining to earth sciences. Examples: geophysical features and
				processes, geology, minerals, sciences dealing with the composition, structure and
				origin of the earth s rocks, risks of earthquakes, volcanic activity, landslides,
				gravity information, soils, permafrost, hydrogeology, erosion
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/health/descript:
Health, health services, human ecology, and safety. Examples: disease and
				illness, factors affecting health, hygiene, substance abuse, mental and physical health,
				health services
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/imageryBaseMaps:
Base maps. Examples: land cover, topographic maps, imagery, unclassified
				images, annotations
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/intelligenceMil:
Military bases, structures, activities. Examples: barracks, training grounds,
				military transportation, information collection
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/inlandWaters/de:
Inland water features, drainage systems and their characteristics. Examples:
				rivers and glaciers, salt lakes, water utilization plans, dams, currents, floods, water
				quality, hydrographic charts
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/location/descri:
Positional information and services. Examples: addresses, geodetic networks,
				control points, postal zones and services, place names
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/oceans/descript:
Features and characteristics of salt water bodies (excluding inland waters).
				Examples: tides, tidal waves, coastal information, reefs
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/planningCadastr:
Information used for appropriate actions for future use of the land. Examples:
				land use maps, zoning maps, cadastral surveys, land ownership
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/society/descrip:
Characteristics of society and cultures. Examples: settlements, anthropology,
				archaeology, education, traditional beliefs, manners and customs, demographic data,
				recreational areas and activities, social impact assessments, crime and justice, census
				information
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/structure/descr:
Man-made construction. Examples: buildings, museums, churches, factories,
				housing, monuments, shops, towers
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/transportation/:
Means and aids for conveying persons and/or goods. Examples: roads,
				airports/airstrips, shipping routes, tunnels, nautical charts, vehicle or vessel
				location, aeronautical charts, railways
gmd:MD_TopicCategoryCode/utilitiesCommun:
Energy, water and waste systems and communications infrastructure and
				services. Examples: hydroelectricity, geothermal, solar and nuclear sources of energy,
				water purification and distribution, sewage collection and disposal, electricity and gas
				distribution, data communication, telecommunication, radio, communication
			networks
gmd:MD_TopologyLevelCode/geometryOnly/de:
Geometry objects without any additional structure which describes
			topology
gmd:MD_TopologyLevelCode/topology1D/desc:
1-dimensional topological complex -- commonly called chain-node
			topology
gmd:MD_TopologyLevelCode/planarGraph/des:
1-dimensional topological complex that is planar. (A planar graph is a graph
				that can be drawn in a plane in such a way that no two edges intersect except at a
				vertex.)
gmd:MD_TopologyLevelCode/fullPlanarGraph:
2-dimensional topological complex that is planar. (A 2-dimensional topological
				complex is commonly called full topology in a cartographic 2D
			environment.)
gmd:MD_TopologyLevelCode/surfaceGraph/de:
1-dimensional topological complex that is isomorphic to a subset of a surface.
				(A geometric complex is isomorphic to a topological complex if their elements are in a
				one-to-one, dimensional-and boundry-preserving correspondence to one
			another.)
gmd:MD_TopologyLevelCode/topology3D/desc: 3 차원 복합 위상. (복합위상은 경계작업 아래 폐쇄된 원시위상 입니다.)
gmd:MD_TopologyLevelCode/abstract/descri: 지정한 임의의 형상 실현이없는 복합 위상
gmd:MX_ScopeCode/software/description: 컴퓨터 프로그램 또는 루틴에 적용되는 정보
